add the ability to download from a choice of mirrors
onion-fec: proper free() when handling errors

Merge branch 'strip-modules'

Conflicts:
	bdb/ant/compile.xml
	bdb/build.xml
	freenet_ext/build.xml
- TODO is already done, and factor contrib package name out into a property
- fred source code was refactored, patches are no longer needed
add bitcollider-core as an external library
- some build notes on the Current Situation
- some tweaks to get compile working on linux
Merge branch 'darwin_fix' of https://github.com/indeyets/contrib-staging into indeyets-darwin_fix
add a TEST_SKIP envvar; update for GMP 5.0.1; use libtool more "properly";
use realpath if that exists (iirc freebsd, darwin don't have readlink -f); refactor get_latest
autoset JAVA_HOME and allow FAIL_FAST option

put proper architecture of libjbigi in filename
tell user what is going on
fix environment variables for mac
